fields.name: Strength
fields.description: Our 8 week Strength program is designed to improve overall strength and to encourage lean muscle growth. Strength combines a mixture of training styles including resistance, weighted, HIIT, LISS, and circuit training sessions. Over the 8 weeks you will transform your overall strength and endurance capabilities, while the variety of training styles keeps your workouts varied and engaging.
fields.program_goals: Improve overall strength. Encourage lean muscle growth.

fields.name: Mobility
fields.description: Our 6 week Mobility program is all about improving your overall mobility. Mobility is key to your overall health and fitness, in this program we teach you to move better, enhance your range of motion and improve your overall performance and functional fitness. Good mobility is the key to performing at your best. Throughout the six weeks you will watch your flexibility, strength, and range of motion improve drastically and reap the benefits this will provide to your other styles of training.
fields.training_styles: Mobility sessions, Core,  Plyometric, Conditioning, Gymnastic strength sessions
fields.program_goals: Improve overall mobility. Increase your flexibility, strength, and range of motion.

fields.name: HIIT
fields.description: Our 6 week program is designed to improve cardiovascular health, endurance, and stamina. With a variety of HIIT and cardio based circuits, you are guaranteed to get your heart pumping! Looking for a break away from heavy lifting? This is the perfect program for you, the basis of this program is high output workouts based around cardio and HIIT exercises with the addition of compound movements to maintain muscle tone throughout. This program guarantees you a fun-filled six weeks of workouts that get you up and moving.
fields.program_goals: Improve cardiovascular health, endurance, and stamina.

fields.name: Nutrition Plan - Vegan
fields.description: Eat more of the foods that you love with our Vegan Nutrition Plan. We've done the heavy lifting so you don't have to! With six weeks access to our vegan customisable nutrition plan you will have access to hundreds of vegan style recipes and meals, which you can pick and choose from on a daily basis. Our dietitians will formulate a meal plan for you based on your fitness goals. Gym Rat Fitness believes in enjoying the foods you love regardless of whether your trying to loose weight or gain muscle. Our nutrition plans are built to be inclusive of all the foods you love, while still hitting your goals and getting you the results you are after.
fields.nutrition_plan_features: Access to hundreds of vegan recipes and meals. Learn to eat what you love while still achieving your goals. Swap up meals on a daily basis to keep things interesting.

fields.name: Elevate Premium Gym Mat
fields.description: Professional Elevate Premium Gym Mat with dimensions 1400 x 600mm and 15mm wide. The Elevate Premium pad provides a solid surface for a wide range of movements, stretching and balance exercises. With a spring-loaded surface, it provides a sufficient level of comfort between the user and the hard surface of the floor. They are used during a wide range of training types. It is suitable not only for aerobic exercise, wellness and fitness, but it has also proved excellent for physiotherapy.

fields.name: Power Exercise Mat
fields.description: Power Exercise Mat is the highest quality mat intended for most group training or individual use. The special material from which it is made does not absorb moisture or dust, and the antibacterial protection system prevents the growth of mycelium and bacteria. It is the most durable mat on the market - it can withstand 5-8 years of intensive use.

fields.name: Movement Yoga Mat
fields.description: This 4mm mat is made from lightweight yet durable rubber with a cool-touch design for premium comfort every time you train. Easy to carry and travel when you roll it up, this mat is finished with our signature logo. (61 x 173cm)

fields.name: Elevate Prime Roller
fields.description: A fine-textured yoga roller is a very effective training aid for rehab, relaxation, or strenght training. Used in yoga, pilates, and resistance training.

fields.name: Power Resistance Loop Bands
fields.description: For the best comfort during your workout, our Loop Bands are your first choice. Super skin-friendly, non-slip and without the annoyance of rolling up you can rely on the Power Resistance Loop Bands. Tear-resistant and durable, these bands will last a lifetime.

fields.name: Power Cross Band
fields.description: Durable and versatile rubber band training. Designed for functional training, either in the gym or fitness club and at home. Power cross bands allow you to practice with various degrees of progressive resistance. These bands are also well suited for training and rehabilitation, as well as strength training.

fields.name: Enhance Chalk Powder
fields.description: A high-quality magnesia chalk block which provides a strong and secure grip. Magnesia is an ideal tool for people practicing gymnasts, weightlifting, CrossFit and climbing so it will be useful everywhere a certain grip is necessary.

fields.name: Enhance Power Grip Gloves
fields.description: This soft and durable material is designed for heavy workouts. Breathable and flexible inserts on the back of the gloves ensure comfort and proper moisture management. Addition of Velcro straps for a strong close.

fields.name: Stylus Grip Straps
fields.description: Stylus Grip Straps are durable training straps that support the grip, especially useful when using larger weights. The belts are made of thick, and strong double-stitched cotton and have a silicone non-slip layer and a soft, neoprene lining around the wrists to improve comfort during training.

fields.name: Made For Life Nutrition Shaker
fields.description: Perfect for mixing protein shakes or even for mixing your other water based supplements like pre-workout products. Our nutrition shaker has a 700ml capacity and a unique top. The shaker is complete with a mesh grill insert, screw on top, clip cap and leak-proof design. Simple, ergonomic, and lightweight makes it perfect to carry on the go.

fields.name: Colour Block Deluxe Shaker
fields.description: Made of BPA free plastic, with a screw on lid built using our leak-free technology. 9000ml measure perfect for protein shakes or pre-workout supplements.

fields.name: Colour Block Contrast Barrel Bag
fields.description: The new addition to the Colour block Gym accessory range. Featuring a large central compartment to store all your fitness essentials and handy hidden zip pocket to store valuables. This gym bag features to carry handles and a large removable shoulder strap.

fields.name: Made For Life Towel
fields.description: Whether you're at the beach or at the gym, this Made For Life Towel is an essential, made from plush cotton for a soft and comfy feel while also being highly absorbent.

fields.name: Enhance Skipping Rope
fields.description: Extremely effective during cardio and HIIT workouts. PVC-coated, wire mounted on bearings provides a slight movement ropes. Removable metal weights on each bracket helps to develop arm muscles. Ergonomically shaped handles provide a firm and comfortable grip.
